responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "2B7A2DC546B8AD33B8B43E92555E71A8", "Not a speck of flesh remains on these bones, but they\'re not dried or bleached. They bear no signs of gnawing, but have odd grooves running along the grain, as though the meat had been surgically separated.")
